    "The study of turnover is a frequently researched topic given the challenges and expenses associated with replacing workers.",
    "In the literature on employee turnover, researchers have long analyzed the impact of both external (labor market conditions) and internal (job satisfaction) factors on an individual's decision to leave their job 66, often through the lens of signature models.",
